data.description: Located in gorgeous historic Homecroft, this home boasts 3400+sqft full of charm & character! Coming up the long driveway w/ updated landscaping is a huge covered front porch & cozy side porch. Plenty of parking w/ heated 2.5 car attached garage & carport. Step in to beautifully maintained hardwood floors! Living room w/ custom built shelves & wood burning fireplace. Dream kitchen w/ ample wood finish cabinetry, tile backsplash & luxury granite counters. TWO eating areas; a nicely sized breakfast area & large dining room w/ ceramic flooring & fireplace. Head upstairs to an office area maximizing storage w/ a closet. Primary bedroom is HUGE w/ 2 walk-in closets & en-suite bathroom! In the partially finished basement, French doors lead to a big laundry room including storage cabinets & utility sink. 2nd set of French doors open to a gym/storage area. Nicely sized office w/ custom built storage. Ideal location w/ shopping & dining nearby, as well as Perry Township schools!
